author: The Critical Drinker
description:
As the Alien franchise endures ever greater indignities, Ray Winstone absolutely dunks on the disastrous shoot for Black Widow, and The Marvels director Nia DaCosta desperately tries to shift the blame, the Open Bar assembles once more. Join me, MauLer, Nerdrotic, Robot Head and BlueCollarLoser for Open Bar episode 154.

title: Open Bar #154 - Alien Earth, Marvels Director's Desperate Cope
